messages.msgSnippet: I read it twice and it still just looked wrong: ***TEACHING TOTS TO TEENS*** Tater tots to teens; that makes sense. Teaching tots to sing; maybe. Feeding tots
messages.messageBody:
I read it twice and it still just looked wrong:

***TEACHING TOTS TO TEENS***


Tater tots to teens; that makes sense.

Teaching tots to sing; maybe.

Feeding tots to teens, not nice (unless tots are assumed to be tater-
variety).


Then I saw what it really meant and realized if failed to make sense
because of the list it was on!

Sandra
